we'll be going through each of these layers step-by-step throughout the course,

49
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:08,750
but with a heavy emphasis on the Power Query and

50
00:03:08,750 --> 00:03:13,725
the data model layers that ultimately support every reporting layer.

